text: Bikmurzino () is a rural locality (a village) in Baygildinsky Selsoviet, Nurimanovsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 150 as of 2010. There are 6 streets. == Geography == It is located 34 km from Krasnaya Gorka, 4 km from Baygildino. == References == Category:Rural localities in Nurimanovsky District
title: Bikmurzino
